{"tid":446230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺不覺怯夫雲畀人鬧幾句就delete ig好小學雞","createTime":"2017-10-24T06:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T08:44:04.000Z","uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3c612e99b7aa00866f7542fc8470bfe97aa8c608","tid":446230,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:26:10.000Z","msg":"利物浦中堅洛夫雲於鬥熱刺時成為輸波罪人，更於早段就被換走，賽後他把instagram個人簡介中的利物浦字樣刪走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在周日作客熱刺的英超大戰，洛夫雲（Dejan Lovren）犯下大錯導致失球，令利物浦最終以1:4大敗一場，自己更在31分鐘就被換出，領隊高普對其表現非常不滿。除了高普之外，名宿及球迷都對他肆意抨擊。 這名克羅地亞國腳賽後把自己的instagram頭像移除，以及在個人簡介中把利物浦字樣刪走，更不讓人留言；似乎今役的打擊對他實在太大，而且不想有利迷在他的instagram生事。 曼聯傳奇門將舒米高指摘高普早早把洛夫雲調離陣，徹底摧毀了他的信心：「高普殺死了這球員，而事實上換人後，利物浦的防守沒有改善。他們整季的防守都是天真的，高普要負責任，他現在做的事，是把所有責任都推到洛夫雲身上，這是不公平的。」"},{"pid":"7a2b80170bf0a344a40a6eb9dfd7a8dde855ddac","tid":446230,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:28:45.000Z","msg":"成日口講YNWA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8988fd9f57de172d9343c79b1f8cceba889cfa30","tid":446230,"uid":2169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"高普殺死這個球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242bd92b408b504aa13a8919060e0bd511e4147a","tid":446230,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"躝"},{"pid":"6b06fa823256685a075ae125b844f151a1f181a0","tid":446230,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:36:58.000Z","msg":"懦夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d806f789fa2a0008c3f5716f0370e86d6d39c92c","tid":446230,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquo